<item>
            <title>[LU-16685] update OSP statfs when max_create_count is set back from 0</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-16685</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;if OSP &lt;tt&gt;max_create_count&lt;/tt&gt; parameter is restored from 0 then we need to refresh OSP local statfs copy to get rid of &lt;tt&gt;OS_STATFS_NOPRECREATE&lt;/tt&gt; flag. Therefore updating &lt;tt&gt;max_create_count&lt;/tt&gt; will be in effect immediately without need to wait for scheduled update&lt;/p&gt;</description>
